Package: rootmech
Type: Package
Title: Plant Root Parameter Fitting
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Gerrit",
             family = "Meijer",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "gjm36@bath.ac.uk",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2815-5480")),
      person(given = "University of Bath",
             role = c("cph")))
Description: Fitting and plotting functions for root parameter fitting.
    Contains functions to plot multisegment power-law probability distributions
    for root diameters, as well as power-law+Weibull fitting of root
    biomechanical parameters such as strength and strain to failure.
